The video was tinted blue at parts but it wasn't all that noticeable, besides that the response time was slow at very high-speed action scenes, resulting in some choppy parts of frames. Other than that the video was good, it wasn't blurred, the color was great so it was pretty good quality. The audio was very clear, not hollow or washed out, definitely line audio. It was quiet a couple of times when it should have been louder but it wasn't action scenes so that was good. Overall decent TS, loved the movie, basically another great upload from raymondhome.
